name: Surfboards, 24X28 (FRAMED PRINT)
description:
Surfboards, (FRAMED)
Printed on Hahnemuhle Fine Art
Baryta 325gsm using archival inks
achieving the quality, look, and feel
of a museum fiber print.

Please allow 5 days to receive all
framed print orders to allow time
for custom matting and framing.

After order you will receive an 
email confirmation with options
for pickup or delivery.

please see information section
on right side of main page for
more details.
